quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,"Mbiɗa woonɗdira ñande ndarnga."
  75,2,"Mbiɗa wooɗndira fittaandu felooru."
  75,3,"Mbela aade sikkat min ndenndintah ƴi'e makko."
  75,4,"Oho kay mbiɗa min kattani fotndude gulle peɗeeli makko."
  75,5,"Kono aade yiɗi konde o wonata saay ye'eso ka ye'eso makko."
  75,6,"Hiɓe laɓndoo : ""Ko honnde woni Ñalaande njoɓdi kuuɗe?"""
  75,7,"Si yitere nde majii."
  75,8,"Lewru ndu nanngaa."
  75,9,"Na'ange e lewru ndenndina."
  75,10,"Ndeen aade wi'a hoɗo dogirde ngoni."
  75,11,"Ala dokdu alah e oon ñalngu."
  75,12,"Koto joom ma ñande heen woni ruttorde nde."
  75,13,"Aade na habre ñande heen ko ardini e golle e ko o leelni ko."
  75,14,"Ko woni ko aade o na seedii e fittaandu makko."
  75,15,"Hay si o addii ngantuuji makko ɗi."
  75,16,"Woto dillin heen ɗemngal ma haa njaawnaɗa e hembo."
  75,17,"Ko minen woodani renndinde mbo e jannginde mbo ma."
  75,18,"Si min njanngii mbo rew e jaŋde makko."
  75,19,"Refti ko e amen fawi firde mbo."
  75,20,"Ala woni ko hoɗon njiɗi aduna jaawɗo o ko gasata."
  75,21,"Ngaccon La'akara."
  75,22,"Je'ece malaaɓe ñande heen na fooyni."
  75,23,"Hoɗe ndaara fa'ade e joom mu' en."
  75,24,"E je'ece ñirɓaniiɗe ñande heen."
  75,25,"Hoɗe cikka ma telline e mu' en musiiba mawɗo."
  75,26,"Ala sindu yottiima bororde."
  75,27,"Wi'e hombo woni moccaoowa."
  75,28,"O yananee ko ɗum ceergal e aduna."
  75,29,"Korlal ngal fiilto e korlal."
  75,30,"Ko ta joom ma ñande heen woni ruttorde."
  75,31,"O gooŋɗinaani o juulaani."
  75,32,"Kono o yeddu o ɗuurnii."
  75,33,"Refti o yahi to koreeji makko hombo wasoo."
  75,34,"Halkaare woodaniima e halkaare."
  75,35,"Refti halkaare kadi woodanii ma e halkaare titi."
  75,36,"Mbele aade o sikku o accete hombo duda."
  75,37,"Mbele o wonaana toɓɓe maniyyu juppateende e rannga."
  75,38,"Refti o wonti heɗɗere o tagi o fonndi."
  75,39,"O waɗI heen kuɓe ɗiɗi dewel e gorel."
  75,40,"Mbele oon hattanaani wuurtin'de maayɓe."
